      "message": "Maybe, the following could be better, as it will tell the users what to do to install the emulator, as documented in https://cloud.google.com/spanner/docs/emulator#gcloud_cli.\n\n\n```\n# this will prompt you to download and install the emulator, if you haven\u0027t installed it yet.\n$ gcloud emulators spanner start\n```",
