      "writtenOn": "2021-03-10T19:51:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "using `gcloud emulators spanner start` to see an emulator is running is probably fine. But I\u0027m not sure about the part of telling people to install. I mean, my intention of this CL is that we can use the bundled gcloud which includes emulator. If we end up telling people to install emulator, then maybe we don\u0027t even need this change.",
      "parentUuid": "7c0a8069_93fa2660",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 14,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 14,
        "endChar": 71
      },
      "revId": "e2f90a4413f0072966fad77538c2eb0d096d5d6e",
